---
import GetInvolvedButtons from "./GetInvolvedButtons.astro";
const paragraphClass = "text-Roboto py-2.5 text-xl";
---

<div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-honey-flower-100 to-honey-flower-300">
    <div
        class="max-w-screen-xl flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-center m-auto"
    >
        <div class="py-10 max-w-xl mx-10 my-auto">
            <div
                class="pb-5 text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-honey-flower-800 font-Trebuchet italic text-left font-bold"
            >
                We're Stronger Together
            </div>
            <p class={paragraphClass}>
                SEIU Local 1107 is the largest union of health care and public
                service employees in Nevada. Together, we're building power to
                raise standards for all workers and protect quality patient care
                and quality public services.
            </p>
            <p class={paragraphClass}>
                We're also showing Nevada what a member-driven, diverse and just
                organization can accomplish when we use our collective voice.
                Nevada home care workers, who lived in poverty for decades while
                serving our seniors and most vulnerable residents, recently
                started joining together through SEIU 1107 and raised their
                minimum wage to $16 an hour, starting in January 2024.
            </p>
            <p class={paragraphClass}>
                SEIU nurses at HCA hospitals in Las Vegas recently won a
                standard setting contract, securing 13.75% raises over three
                years. And soon, our state's public workers will take center
                stage, protecting the critical public services that all Nevadans
                count on as we negotiate improvements in 2024.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="hidden lg:block">
            <GetInvolvedButtons />
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="block lg:hidden">
    <GetInvolvedButtons />
</div>
